{{Infobox Union |name= CLTT |country= [[Chad]] |affiliation= [[International Trade Union Confederation|ITUC]] |members= |full_name= Free Confederation of Chadian Workers |native_name= Confédération Libre des Travailleurs du Tchad |image= |founded= 1991 |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[N'Djaména]], Chad |people= [[Brahim Bakass]], president |website= |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''Free Confederation of Chadian Workers''' (CLTT) is a [[trade union]] centre in [[Chad]]. It was formed in 1991 by members from the dissolved [[National Confederation of Trade Unions of Chad]].
The CLTT is affiliated with the [[International Trade Union Confederation]].
