'''Heeresnachrichtenamt''' (Army Intelligence Office) is an [[intelligence agency]] of the [[Military of Austria|Austrian Armed Forces]].<ref Name="IIHA">{{cite book|title=The journal of intelligence history|last= IIHA|author2=International Intelligence History Association|year=2002|publisher=LIT Verlag Münster|isbn=3-8258-0646-4|page=25|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=deqkBXe0RVYC&pg=PA25&dq=Heeresnachrichtenamt&hl=en&ei=VPPKTI7uDYO8lQe59NjqAQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCUQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Heeresnachrichtenamt&f=false }}</ref> Heeresnachrichtenamt researches information on military operations and projects abroad and conducts data analysis of gathered [[military intelligence|intelligence]]. The service maintains branch offices in [[Linz]], [[Graz]] and [[Klagenfurt]].

