The '''Irbit Bike Show''' (Ирбитский байк слёт) is held every year at the end of July. It is organised by the local bike club as a celebration of the town's importance as a manufacturer of heavy motorcycles (see [[IMZ-Ural]]) in both the [[Soviet Union]] and [[Russia]]. Thousands of riders from throughout the [[Sverdlovsk Oblast|Sverdlovsk region]] and other parts of Russia attend, and increasingly more foreign riders are attending.



