The '''''Malawi Government Gazette''''' is the [[government gazette]] of [[Malawi]].

The ''Gazette'' has been published since independence from Britain in July 1964.<ref>[http://www.crl.edu/collections/topics/official-gazettes/search?titleID=t338&pc=1 MALAWI] CRL Foreign Official Gazette Database, 2014. Retrieved 28 May 2014. [https://www.webcitation.org/6PtsU1gm8?url=http://www.crl.edu/collections/topics/official-gazettes/search?titleID%3Dt338%26pc%3D1 Archived here.]</ref> Copies up to 1988 may be found in the collections of the [[British Library]].<ref>[http://www.bl.uk/reshelp/findhelpregion/africa/malawi/acmalawi/ Malawi official publications] British Library, 2014. Retrieved 28 May 2014.</ref>

